
'''= to enable mobile workers to work from any of the spaces in the network with one single account'''

URL = http://copass.org/


=Description=

"The way we work, travel and meet people has been changing like never before these last few years. 

Coworking spaces, fablabs, hackerspaces and other likeminded collaborative spaces offer fantastic ecosystems and infrastructures for creative minds. We think it's time to connect the dots. It's time to join forces and to create the first global network of independent spaces. We think that connecting these communities and ecosystem will open doors for a whole new world of work.  

The idea of Copass is to enable mobile workers to work from any of the spaces in the network with one single account and at discounted fares. Copass is under construction. More than 70 spaces have already joined the movement. We can't wait to start copassing."
(http://copass.org/)


